Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just supposed to be an ordinary third grader,\N but then a small incident happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I received was a courageous heart.\N What I gained were magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our constantly opposing feelings\N have vanished into the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer sure if the path I'm stumbling\N down is truly the right one or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.69,0:00:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there are times when\N people lose their way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the mistakes I made in the past are having an\N effect on me now, and will affect me in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha will now begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:01:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I was always so uneasy that I was shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Hugging my knees in the corner of my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I was afraid of knowing the "truth"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}and closed the door to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}Through a kind lie, I discovered where I should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I fled and took refuge in my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}No one knows of the lonely sea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.51,0:01:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}being dyed a deep blue color
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}that hides my loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}With wholehearted feelings, I wounded your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}The secret within your eyes makes me want to soak it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I'll bring the truth behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}your smile with a warm love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}If I touch it, the warmth that seems so breakable will
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}break away from its past and overflow.\NBecause you're always by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}I will no longer be puzzled over the shadow of loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Return, Bardiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.16,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate! Stop! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop, stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop... stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Raising Heart is a device that can\N endure large amounts of energy, yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To damage it this badly in only one impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could that girl's magical powers\N have conflicted with Nanoha's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No... even if they did, that still wouldn't\N explain this amount of damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That really was... the Jewel Seed's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuno-kun... is the Raising Heart all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.29,0:05:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The damage is pretty extensive,\N but I'm sure it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its automatic regeneration system is working,\N so it should be fully recovered by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.83,0:05:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... because the Raising Heart protected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.97,0:05:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... Raising Heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Fate! We're almost done...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.87,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Arf...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to report back to Mother on my current status\N tomorrow, so... I'll have to get better soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because if I went home in this shape,\N I'm sure I'd worry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would she really... worry about you? That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother is just a little awkward, that's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell how she really feels towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:07:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're only going to give your report,\N I think it'd be okay if I went alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... never really listened to\N what you had to say, did she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're such a kind, good girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think tomorrow will go okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the short amount of time we've been here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we've managed to collect four Lost\N Logia... or rather, Jewel Seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll be full of praise for you,\N since there's nothing to be angry about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Nanoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are up early today. What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... my eyes just felt like opening this early, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... he went long distance running\N with Dad this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't bother you... do you mind if I watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it'll be all that interesting, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine with me! I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nanoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yuuno-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong? You're up pretty early...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ahh... I just woke up this early, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, and Yuuno-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been doing a lot of thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... really curious about that girl... Fate-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.28,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's so strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And even though she seems so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...she has such beautiful, kind eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet... for some reason, she really\N looks... incredibly sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really believe she has a reason for doing all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her reason for collecting the Jewel Seeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why... I want to talk with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So... in order to do that, I'm going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be fine for a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet candies, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will this really make that woman happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but it's the thought that\N counts for this kind of thing, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dimensional Transfer. Dimensional Coordinates -\N876C 4419 3312 D699 3583 A1460 779 F3125.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:11:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open, O Door of Invitation to the Garden of Time.\N To the household of the Testarossa family!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's our status, people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we still on the proper heading this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Presently, we're cruising at a constant\N level three nautical velocity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By my calculations, we're planned to arrive at\N our target dimension in roughly 160 vecs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There hasn't been any noticeable movement since that\N small-scale dimensional disturbance they caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the danger of those two people\N colliding again is extraordinarily high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.77,0:12:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Here you are, Captain Lindy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was on a small scale, outbreaks of\N dimensional disturbances... can be quite problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets too dangerous, we'll just have to hurry directly\N to the scene of the disturbance. Right, Chrono?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite aware of our situation, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mere four...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terribly disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, Fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are my daughter. The sole offspring\N of the Great Mage Precia Testarossa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.95,0:13:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing is impossible for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what it may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We must complete anything\N we begin, in all respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made me wait this long...\N only for these meager results...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I could have welcomed\N you home with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust that you understand, Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why... that's why I want you to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never disappoint me again like you've done today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell... what the hell is wrong with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just too cruel! That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That woman... that woman claims\N to be Fate's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't the first time she's been cruel to Fate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just too much this time!\N What the hell is wrong with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.86,0:15:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are the Lost Logia... the Jewel Seeds worth all that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lost Logia are essential to\N the fruition of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're central to everything... the purity of the\N Jewel Seeds goes far beyond any other substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a kind girl, so you might hesitate\N when trying to collect them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something gets in your way, destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the power to do so lies within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go, bring them to me, my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My charming Fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:16:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I'll be going then, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, be sure to delight me with your offerings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fate, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing, Arf...?\N I'm fine... perfectly fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...! If I had known something\N like this would happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after you got what she wanted, I never thought\N she'd do something this cruel to you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known, I would've stopped you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... was thinking of me when she did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! This was cruel and unusual punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... after all, we're mother and daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Jewel Seeds are\N really important to Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother's always been so full of sadness...\N so I want to do something that might cheer her up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.23,0:17:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arf, please. I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...once I return with every Jewel Seed,\N even Mother will smile again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.86,0:17:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll go back to being the kind mother\N she used to be, so long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.79,0:18:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm sure she'll even be kind to you, Arf...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...make no mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bardiche, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.80,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Recovery complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You really gave it your all. You're great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense it... even I can tell that it's around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It'll soon be activated, and it's very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raising Heart... you're all better, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.71,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Condition green.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you give me your best again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.92,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency Barrier! Expand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! They're pretty arrogant,\N already putting up a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The creature this time is stronger than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that girl's here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuno-kun! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:32.96,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Flier Fin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly, Raising Heart! We have to go higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:39.17,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arc Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Bardiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.20,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Arc Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.52,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:21:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Raising Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crush it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Divine...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.12,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,...Buster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierce it, thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:29.72,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Smasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.70,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Mode, Set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.83,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing Form, Set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jewel Seed Serial VII!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we can't put any more\N stress on the Jewel Seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If it turns out like the one last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.79,0:22:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel sorry for my Raising Heart and your Bardiche.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I won't yield this match to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.93,0:22:28.33,Bardiche,,0000,0000,0000,,Device Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to talk with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:35.86,Raising Heart,,0000,0000,0000,,Device Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win... and you understand that I'm not just\N some innocent girl mixed up in all of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will you let me listen to your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing combat here is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a government official from the Time-Space\N Administration Bureau, Chrono Hallaoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.49,0:23:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need a detailed explanation about this from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. I was stumbling
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.91,0:23:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and losing my way on my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since you were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.35,0:23:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the silver wind came looking for\N two who were lacking something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:24:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the cellophane sea and forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.30,0:24:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just crying in our city that's\N nothing more than a diorama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you held out to me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.58,0:24:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the ever-swaying years,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt you looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.95,0:24:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I had finally, finally found the secret key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish. Gather the lemon-colored
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.19,0:24:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drops of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.86,0:24:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to gently light the path you're walking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.85,0:24:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a little wish, even if it's a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.77,0:24:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you say you can't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.39,0:24:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then remember that because you were there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.22,0:25:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to keep smiling and stay happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.87,0:25:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}After hearing some things from\N the third mage, Chrono-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.28,0:25:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}...the true identity of the Jewel\N Seeds has finally become clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.12,0:25:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}...and things have\N gotten really serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}And I've personally learned\N something extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.93,0:25:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Yuuno-kun is... Yuuno-kun is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.09,0:25:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Next time on\N Magical Girl Lyrical Nanoha:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.72,0:25:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Episode Eight:\N There's a Really Big Crisis?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}I, Lyrical Magical,\N will do my best!
